                  </persName>) was again indicted for<rs id="t18530815-890-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18530815-890-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18530815-890-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> unlawfully uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
